Bola Tinubu, the presidential candidate of the All Progressives Congress (APC), and Kashim Shettima, his running mate, were in Zamfara on Saturday for the party’s campaign rally. Bello Matawalle, the Zamfara governor; Abdullahi Adamu, APC national chairperson, and other party stakeholders were in attendance. Below are pictures from the event.              PDP CAMPAIGNS IN KEBBI Meanwhile, Atiku Abubakar, presidential candidate of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP), and Ifeanyi Okowa, his running, were in Kebbi for the party’s rally. Iyorchia Ayu, PDP national chair, and Aminu Tambuwal, governor of Sokoto, were also in attendance. See photos below.           